{"tid":1285283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係攰啦,所以決定","createTime":"2019-07-04T13:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T00:30:46.000Z","uid":204625,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d93f5962d9eea55bff15c92caf83145c379d9ad3","tid":1285283,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:40:02.000Z","msg":"今日淨係跑2km<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽朝先跑返5km<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭唔一定係日日搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但運動一定要日日做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每日做小小已經好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做運動所生產嘅安多芬係你嘅好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n安多芬可以帶畀你正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每日做少少運動就會每日加幾粒正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提升心理質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁先可以同班狗官鬥長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到佢哋仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入咗嚟睇既巴絲打<br />\n就由聽日起每日都係全民運動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e179c771cd86b2b1f406b60b2c21db66071853eb","tid":1285283,"uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f47ed754508b0660a7cfaa7292fedbe4ad0f87a","tid":1285283,"uid":260747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T